  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=faedeb93&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FfbRX0iaT8Egeaq2icVgD7U0gPdibJbetTgAU7GMcn6JumJvvoUIz5NZrYX1xRIzJV72F2ibyQqmk2RUPlsKRJb7hsg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"color: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 6px 6px;padding: 6px 6px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-radius: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #646a73;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 0px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">大家好，我是歸藏（guizang），今天教大家解决 Nana Banana 出图最大的问题。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #646a73;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 0px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">Nano Banana 已经非常强了，但是最近大家普遍用的时候两个问题非常影响可用性：</span></span></p>\n   <p></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style: none;font-weight: normal;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 16px 0;line-height: 30px;padding-left: 0px;color: inherit;font-size: 16px;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;line-height: 30px;paddingLeft: 20px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"font-size: 16px;color: #000;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 6px;height: 6px;border-radius: 50%;background-color: #000000;margin-bottom: 2px;background-color: rgba(20, 86, 240, 1);margin-right: 8px;\"></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">首先是分辨率较低，这个没啥办法，跟模型相关。</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"font-size: 16px;color: #000;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 6px;height: 6px;border-radius: 50%;background-color: #000000;margin-bottom: 2px;background-color: rgba(20, 86, 240, 1);margin-right: 8px;\"></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后是出图比例高度不可控，本来连续的图片因为比例不一样很难用到生产中。</span></span></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #646a73;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 0px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我最近也一直在想怎么解决这个问题，前几天心里隐约有个想法，今天终于搞定了，话不多说先看结果：</span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n    <p style=\"display: inline-block;margin: 0px;box-shadow: none;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100008379\" data-ratio=\"0.5722222222222222\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;border: none;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d6f9fcae&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FfbRX0iaT8Egeaq2icVgD7U0gPdibJbetTgAicaS3E2cvbsLAwmicS9tNymESle7AXre3nLZXz5zL96m6jAszfceHBBg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #646a73;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 0px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们先来看一下方法的原理以及应该怎么做。</span></span></p>\n   <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   <div></div>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #646a73;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 0px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">用 Nano Banana 多的朋友可能发现了，就是 Nano Banana 在有多张图片输入的时候，输出图的比例会跟其中一张相同，只不过这个过程很不可控。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #646a73;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 0px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我一直想能不能从这一点去突破，今天早上刚好看到一个英雄所见略同的，GLif 尝试用垫图的方式控制 Nana Banana 纯生成图片的比例，没想到真行，不过他们只支持文生图。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #646a73;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 0px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">藏师傅经过一顿科研发现已经生成好的图片也可以用这个方式去修改，</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-weight: bold;color: #000000 !important;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">你可以用这个方法重新跑一次拯救你的旧图，而且新生成的图片也可以再跑一次重新定义生成比例。</span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n    <p style=\"display: inline-block;margin: 0px;box-shadow: none;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100008380\" data-ratio=\"0.9120370370370371\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;border: none;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a34216d8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FfbRX0iaT8Egeaq2icVgD7U0gPdibJbetTgA5hoUjCYuPyElWSfs0KErBewbDLsicdewccyj7dfORvJ3p0WlXdDq9UQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #646a73;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 0px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们需要两张图片来完成这个任务：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #646a73;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 0px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">首先肯定是你</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-weight: bold;color: #000000 !important;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">之前生成的结果图，或者是你从其他地方获取的图片</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">只是想更改比例也可以的。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #646a73;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 0px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如我前几天做的这个 AI 书法舞女，由于书法字体每张截图都不一样大，导致生成的图片大小也不一样，很烦，为了生成视频我还得自己裁切，这样就容易丢失信息。</span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n    <p style=\"display: inline-block;margin: 0px;box-shadow: none;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100008377\" data-ratio=\"0.9388888888888889\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;border: none;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d442c404&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FfbRX0iaT8Egeaq2icVgD7U0gPdibJbetTgAIVTK2hrUTLV863ghrTjswUq9xj5uLOElobMr0eyboJ3pFQMt4PoiaEw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #646a73;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 0px 0;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7106084885198307332;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后我们需要一张比例参考图，让 Nano Banana 将我们原来的内容替换到这张参考图上。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-h